    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, delivering a 8,400 RPM redline through a tactile 6-speed manual transmission. The mechanical vitals are strong, with the critical rod bearing service and throttle actuator replacements already performed. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and the M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring neutral handling and precise turn-in. The hydraulic steering remains communicative and free of play. While the exterior shows the light patina of a well-loved performance machine, the drivetrain remains tight, the VANOS system is quiet, and the exhaust note is pure. A mechanically sound specimen ready for the backroads.",
